类 PairedStats

    public class PairedStats
extends Object
implements RevisionHandler
    A class for storing stats on a paired comparison (t-test and correlation)
    版本:
    $Revision: 1.10 $
    作者:
    Len Trigg (trigg@cs.waikato.ac.nz)
